1. Integration Overview
1.1 Business Context
The Conference Room Booking System integrates with Dynamics 365 Business Central to provide:

Room resource management within Business Central's item/resource system

Booking synchronization between web application and Business Central

Financial integration for billing and cost allocation

Employee directory synchronization with Business Central contacts

