8. Troubleshooting & Best Practices
8.1 Common Issues & Solutions
Issue	Symptoms	Solution
Symbols not loading	"Could not find package" errors	Run al package cache in AL directory
Publish failures	Error 500 on publish	Check BC service running; restart container
Test failures	Tests pass locally but fail in CI	Ensure test isolation; use Any codeunit
Performance issues	Slow page loads in BC	Add indexes; optimize AL queries
Upgrade failures	Data migration errors	Implement upgrade codeunits with error handling
8.2 AL Development Best Practices
Use explicit variable declaration: Avoid implicit with statements

Implement error handling: Use if not Rec.Find() then exit; patterns

Optimize database calls: Minimize loops with record sets

Follow security patterns: Use permission sets for data access

Document complex logic: Add comments for business rules

Test edge cases: Include boundary value tests

Plan for upgrades: Always include upgrade codeunits

Monitor performance: Use SQL profiling for slow queries

